This is an example of how to implement pytest for a simple program
All tests must start with test_

==VSCODE==
Open test file
Then press CTRL+SHIFT+p
And search Python: COnfigure tests
Select this then select pytest and then . Root Directory
Navigate to the beaker in the left hand side of the window and the tests should be displayed there you may need to refresh

==Terminal==
Naviagte to folder with test file
Run pytest (file name) -v
